# Calibration — private user calibration files must never be committed.
# The bundled VelonLabs Reference Snapshot in skills/inference/_calibration_data.py
# is the only calibration file that lives in the repo. Everything else is
# user-specific (their trade history, their VelonLabs API key, their custom
# JSON) and stays local.
.master-trading/
calibration_*.json
!skills/inference/_calibration_data.py
*.calibration.json
my_calibration.json
trades_*.csv
trade_history*.csv

